item.title: Help with PI Cache
item.dc:creator: @frozon566 frozon566
item.description:
@frozon566 wrote:

I do believe you packaged your cache wrong, make an empty zip file and put everything into it, i think what happens is your server wants to look in (as an example)

C:\InvCoalition\maps\mapConfig.txt

but instead the packaging adds an extra folder or somethin’ so it ends up with

C:\InvCoalition\InvCoalition\maps\mapConfig.txt

Read full topic
